00:49:36,049 --> 00:49:38,425
I'll be able to help out
Gerry while I'm in here.

764
00:49:41,847 --> 00:49:43,138
Danny's dead, Gerry.

765
00:49:44,432 --> 00:49:45,516
What?

766
00:49:48,019 --> 00:49:50,563
They found his body on waste ground.

767
00:49:51,189 --> 00:49:53,858
The IRA said he was
