768
00:49:57,779 --> 00:50:00,281
I sent a mass card from the family.

769
00:50:04,828 --> 00:50:06,704
This one'll not go to school
since you've been away.

770
00:50:06,955 --> 00:50:08,664
Hey, you go to school for your mummy.

771
00:50:09,040 --> 00:50:10,416
Yes, Daddy.

772
00:50:11,418 --> 00:50:13,627
Daddy, when will you be home?

773
00:50:15,964 --> 00:50:18,883
I've pressed your Sunday
