785
00:50:54,127 --> 00:50:56,503
Your word will be
good enough for the court.

786
00:50:58,673 --> 00:51:00,007
Yes, sir.

787
00:51:04,763 --> 00:51:06,722
Kill the bastards!
Kill 'em!

788
00:51:12,479 --> 00:51:14,355
Shoot the bastards!

789
00:51:29,037 --> 00:51:30,663
Call number one.

790
00:51:34,292 --> 00:51:36,418
Let's go.
Jesus, it's a nightmare, Guiseppe.

791
00:51:36,503 --> 00:51:38,587
Just stay calm,
be on your best behavior,

792
00:51:38,672 --> 00:51:40,965
and this'll be behind us soon.

793
00:51:41,132 --> 00:51:42,883
That's it, come on.

794
00:51:43,385 --> 00:51:45,177
Say a wee prayer.

795
00:51:47,555 --> 00:51:49,390
It will be all right.

796
00:51:59,234 --> 00:52:02,027
All rise.

797
00:52:20,797 --> 00:52:24,883
Sir Michael Hagerty will present
the case on behalf of the Crown.

798
00:52:29,597 --> 00:52:33,267
There are two series of charges
here, ladies and gentlemen.

799
00:52:33,685 --> 00:52:35,978
The four defendants in front

800
00:52:36,938 --> 00:52:41,650
are charged with 11 counts in relation
to the explosion of the Guildford pub

801
00:52:41,735 --> 00:52:44,028
and the murders of five people.

802
00:52:44,320 --> 00:52:47,448
The Crown will show
that these were the bombers.

803
00:52:47,866 --> 00:52:50,075
The seven defendants behind

804
00:52:50,160 --> 00:52:52,202
are charged with the
possession of explosives.

805
00:52:52,287 --> 00:52:53,996
They're not charged with murder.

806
00:52:54,622 --> 00:52:56,373
The Crown's case against them is

807
00:52:56,458 --> 00:52:59,084
that they are a support
network for the bombers,

808
00:52:59,169 --> 00:53:01,128
and as such should be
considered totally independent.

809
00:53:01,212 --> 00:53:03,088
Control yourself.
Pay attention.

810
00:53:04,466 --> 00:53:07,634
My first witness is
Inspector Robert Dixon.

811
00:53:08,970 --> 00:53:11,805
"I swear by Almighty God that the
evidence I give shall be the truth,

812
00:53:11,890 --> 00:53:14,767
"the whole truth
and nothing but the truth."

813
00:53:17,812 --> 00:53:21,273
Inspector, why do you believe
these four are the bombers?

814
00:53:23,109 --> 00:53:27,196
First Hill, then Conlon,
Armstrong, Richardson,

815
00:53:27,280 --> 00:53:29,281
confessed to the bombing.

816
00:53:29,824 --> 00:53:31,492
They are the IRA's ASU.

817
00:53:31,701 --> 00:53:34,161
Can you explain ASUs for us?

818
00:53:34,621 --> 00:53:35,954
Active Service Unit.

819
00:53:36,039 --> 00:53:37,414
They are the elite of the IRA,

820
00:53:37,499 --> 00:53:39,291
those who carry out the
bombings and the shootings.

821
00:53:39,834 --> 00:53:41,251
Very often they are combat veterans

822
00:53:41,336 --> 00:53:44,421
with previous experience
of shooting at soldiers

823
00:53:44,506 --> 00:53:45,547
and planting explosives.

824
00:53:45,632 --> 00:53:48,467
And the others,
Annie Maguire and her family?

825
00:53:48,927 --> 00:53:50,928
They are the IRA's support network.

826
00:53:51,012 --> 00:53:52,679
They store...

827
00:53:52,847 --> 00:53:55,682
Their families, friends, they
store the weapons and explosives

828
00:53:55,767 --> 00:53:59,103
and they provide
what we call safe houses.

829
00:54:00,522 --> 00:54:01,814
Thank you, Inspector.

830
00:54:03,858 --> 00:54:05,567
Inspector, these people were arrested

831
00:54:05,652 --> 00:54:09,029
two days after the Prevention of
Terrorism Act was introduced.

832
00:54:09,697 --> 00:54:11,031
That's correct.

833
00:54:11,366 --> 00:54:14,034
Can you explain, please, the powers
that this gives to the police?

834
00:54:14,536 --> 00:54:16,954
It permits us to hold
suspected terrorists

835
00:54:17,038 --> 00:54:19,164
for a period of up to seven days.

836
00:54:19,249 --> 00:54:21,792
Quite extraordinary powers
in a democracy.

837
00:54:21,960 --> 00:54:23,585
Quite difficult, I would've
thought, for the police

838
00:54:23,670 --> 00:54:26,213
to resist the temptation to
deal forcibly with people.

839
00:54:26,297 --> 00:54:27,297
Objection.

840
00:54:27,382 --> 00:54:29,883
People whom they suspect of
the biggest bombing campaign

841
00:54:29,968 --> 00:54:32,261
on British mainland
since the Second World War.

842
00:54:32,345 --> 00:54:33,971
Objection.
My Lord, I really must...

843
00:54:34,389 --> 00:54:35,430
Get to the point!

844
00:54:35,557 --> 00:54:37,516
Now, this bombing campaign

845
00:54:37,600 --> 00:54:41,145
struck deep into the British
people's sense of security.

846
00:54:41,896 --> 00:54:44,815
The people looked to you, Inspector,
to find those responsible.

847
00:54:44,899 --> 00:54:45,941
Yes.

848
00:54:47,026 --> 00:54:48,819
You must have been under
the most intense pressure.

849
00:54:49,821 --> 00:54:50,904
That's my job.

850
00:54:51,948 --> 00:54:54,116
Now, all of the defendants claim...

851
00:54:54,200 --> 00:54:57,244
Including young Patrick
Maguire, aged just 14.

852
00:54:57,787 --> 00:55:00,330
Patrick, would you stand up, please?

853
00:55:01,791 --> 00:55:04,251
Thank you.
All of the defendants claim

854
00:55:04,794 --> 00:55:08,463
that they were subjected to physical and
