01:04:24,228 --> 01:04:25,353
Guilty as charged.

1015
01:04:28,816 --> 01:04:30,817
Hang the Irish bastards!

1016
01:04:32,737 --> 01:04:34,904
Order! Silence!

1017
01:04:37,533 --> 01:04:39,367
String 'em up!

1018
01:04:46,333 --> 01:04:49,002
Gerard Patrick Conlon.

1019
01:04:50,171 --> 01:04:51,463
Stand up.

1020
01:04:54,759 --> 01:04:58,011
I feel it is my duty to wonder aloud

1021
01:04:58,679 --> 01:05:01,931
why you were not charged
with treason to the Crown,

1022
01:05:03,184 --> 01:05:06,352
a charge that carries a
penalty of death by hanging.

1023
01:05:08,272 --> 01:05:12,108
A sentence I would have had
no difficulty in passing

1024
01:05:12,193 --> 01:05:13,693
in this case.

1025
01:05:15,696 --> 01:05:17,322
I sentence you to life imprisonment

1026
01:05:18,699 --> 01:05:20,450
and I instruct that you shall serve

1027
01:05:20,993 --> 01:05:23,578
A minimum of 30 years.

1028
01:05:25,456 --> 01:05:26,956
Take him down.

1029
01:05:29,460 --> 01:05:30,877
Come on, Son.

1030
01:05:38,719 --> 01:05:40,011
Help me.

1031
01:05:49,688 --> 01:05:51,898
Paul Michael Hill.

1032
01:05:54,527 --> 01:05:58,446
In my view, your crime is such that

1033
01:05:58,531 --> 01:05:59,989
life shall mean life.

1034
01:06:01,784 --> 01:06:05,328
Annie Maguire, I recommend
you serve 14 years!

1035
01:06:05,412 --> 01:06:07,163
What have I done, for Christ's sake?

1036
01:06:07,248 --> 01:06:08,748
Take her down!

1037
01:06:08,999 --> 01:06:10,750
Guiseppe Conlon, 12 years.

1038
01:06:10,835 --> 01:06:12,669
No! No, my
husband's innocent!

1039
01:06:12,753 --> 01:06:14,045
Lord have mercy on you!

1040
01:06:14,129 --> 01:06:17,048
Patrick Joseph Armstrong, 30 years.

1041
01:06:23,305 --> 01:06:26,391
Carole Richardson, 30 years.

1042
01:07:22,448 --> 01:07:24,157
Our case was so insane

1043
01:07:24,241 --> 01:07:26,451
that if you made it up,
nobody would believe it.

1044
01:07:26,535 --> 01:07:29,746
Look, Gareth, I know people say
that I'm a compulsive storyteller

1045
01:07:29,830 --> 01:07:31,623
and nobody believed
a word I said in court,

1046
01:07:31,707 --> 01:07:34,000
but, Gareth, Charlie Burke did exist.

1047
01:07:34,084 --> 01:07:36,419
He's not just a figment
of my imagination.

1048
01:07:41,008 --> 01:07:42,175
Sorry.

1049
01:07:54,980 --> 01:07:56,940
We were shipped off
to Park Royal Prison,

1050
01:07:57,483 --> 01:08:01,444
an old Victorian fortress where the Britain's
most dangerous criminals were held

1051
01:08:01,528 --> 01:08:03,738
in the maximum-security wing.

1052
01:08:04,114 --> 01:08:06,032
- Place of birth.
- Belfast.

1053
01:08:06,367 --> 01:08:07,659
Then you're British.

1054
01:08:07,743 --> 01:08:08,952
This is your home
for the rest of your life.

1055
01:08:09,078 --> 01:08:11,454
So accept it and get on with it.
Right, come this way.

1056
01:08:11,789 --> 01:08:13,164
The chief warder, Barker,

1057
01:08:13,248 --> 01:08:16,292
gave us blue denim uniforms
with yellow stripes.

1058
01:08:16,377 --> 01:08:17,794
We were Category A,

1059
01:08:17,878 --> 01:08:21,381
the highest security class along
with the rapists and murderers.

1060
01:08:22,216 --> 01:08:24,133
My father said
we'd fight for an appeal,

1061
