but I didn't want to know
about the legal system.

1062
01:08:27,221 --> 01:08:28,388
I'm going back to the cell.

1063
01:08:28,472 --> 01:08:30,223
Come on. Follow me.

1064
01:08:40,776 --> 01:08:42,318
Come on, Gerry.

1065
01:08:44,154 --> 01:08:46,906
Hey, Ronnie.
There's those Irish bastards, Ronnie.

1066
01:08:49,368 --> 01:08:50,535
Irish scum.

1067
01:08:51,286 --> 01:08:53,621
My name's Guiseppe Conlon.
I'm an innocent man.

1068
01:08:53,706 --> 01:08:55,164
So is my son.

1069
01:08:56,166 --> 01:08:57,542
We shouldn't even be in here.

1070
01:08:57,751 --> 01:08:59,377
Get that fucking scum off my floor.

1071
01:09:24,361 --> 01:09:26,279
They must know they've made a mistake.

1072
01:09:26,363 --> 01:09:27,905
No, they don't.

1073
01:09:27,990 --> 01:09:31,534
The proof of our innocence
must be there in the evidence.

1074
01:09:31,618 --> 01:09:33,077
We have to fight 'em to get an appeal.

1075
01:09:35,039 --> 01:09:36,289
I'll speak to Father Wilson.

1076
01:09:36,582 --> 01:09:38,374
Speak to everybody.

1077
01:09:38,792 --> 01:09:41,461
We'll write letters from in here.
Start a campaign.

1078
01:09:42,755 --> 01:09:43,963
Have they been treating you all right?

1079
01:09:44,423 --> 01:09:45,798
Aye, fine. Fine.

1080
01:09:46,925 --> 01:09:48,051
Have they, Son?

1081
01:09:49,511 --> 01:09:51,387
Aye. No problem.

1082
01:10:09,031 --> 01:10:11,074
Forgot the dessert spoons.

1083
01:10:12,701 --> 01:10:13,951
There we go.

1084
01:10:24,004 --> 01:10:26,672
Mmm. These chips
are not bad.

1085
01:10:33,639 --> 01:10:35,098
Now don't you despair, Son.

1086
01:10:35,182 --> 01:10:37,016
Never mind about
"don't despair."

1087
01:10:37,434 --> 01:10:38,518
What?

1088
01:10:39,144 --> 01:10:41,312
I mean, we're innocent, we
can't even go out of the cell.

1089
01:10:43,315 --> 01:10:45,608
You're better off being guilty.

1090
01:10:45,859 --> 01:10:47,819
At least you get some respect.

1091
01:10:49,071 --> 01:10:52,031
Landing officers
on the threes for exercise.

1092
01:10:52,116 --> 01:10:53,991
Here, you can have my chips.

1093
01:10:54,201 --> 01:10:56,869
Landing officers
on the threes for exercise.

1094
